{"tid":1706511,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"對於話要杯葛區選既人","createTime":"2019-11-11T06:06:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T08:15:28.000Z","uid":120760,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"eab040da08c0ec528032713711c31e6ba9d16beb","tid":1706511,"uid":120760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T06:06:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">如果</span></span>今次區議會選舉<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">仲可以順利舉行</span></span>既話<br />\n<br />\n一定要去<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">投票</span></span>投泛民主派別既人<br />\n<br />\n既然都可以做到<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">黃色經濟圈</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解唔可以<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">利用同一方法</span></span>去支持區議會選舉既泛民主派陣型？<br />\n<br />\n藍色少左區議會板塊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就會<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">少左一筆</span></span>公開既<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">可從中抽水</span></span>既款項<br />\n<br />\n少左地區樁腳<br />\n<br />\n底層就會<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有機會</span></span>同樓上果班高貴建制派人士<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不和</span></span><br />\n<br />\n何樂而不為？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你地話去參加選舉既人係食人血饅頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但有無考慮過泛民主派搶走左區會板塊後<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">對現在既運動有更好既幫助</span></span>？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">剩係</span></span>睇短期結果<br />\n<br />\n記得<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要睇埋</span></span>長遠既效益<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">水滴石穿, 聚沙成塔</span><br />\n<br />\n只要能搞到對方疲倦都係我地<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">邁向勝利既其中一步</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88b8ff032457f1171cf76767e1de1ae47b5ac814","tid":1706511,"uid":120760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T07:05:38.000Z","msg":"推一下"},{"pid":"1ac7a0124745504d024a456ce74b61c1d008dabe","tid":1706511,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T17:26:44.000Z","msg":"岩，點解要比錢對方貪腐"},{"pid":"3eb8c0d4e4e32e4595637ba88013367ff2c8a8b6","tid":1706511,"uid":308414,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T17:28:05.000Z","msg":"有得投票就投<br />\n投唔到就算撚數"},{"pid":"e715cace73b891eccddab6c2632911d4fa666d71","tid":1706511,"uid":120760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T08:15:28.000Z","msg":"推一下"}]}